-- Turkey's Vakifbank secures $995 mln syndicated loan 
-- 
-- Thu Apr 17, 2014 04:26AM EDT
-- None



ISTANBUL, April 17 (Reuters) - Turkey's Vakifbank <VAKBN.IS> secured a one-year syndicated loan in two tranches of $270.5 million and 525 million euros ($724.84 million) from international markets, the bank said on Thursday.

